Szczawnica-Zdrój.title: Szczawnica-Zdrój
Szczawnica-Zdrój.byline: Szczawnica is a spa town in Małopolskie Province in the mountains of southern Poland.

Szczecin.title: Szczecin
Szczecin.byline: Szczecin, (pronounced Shchetsin, German: Stettin, Latin: Stetinum) is a maritime port city and the capital of Zachodniopomorskie in Poland.

Szczyrk.title: Szczyrk
Szczyrk.byline: Szczyrk is a winter sport resort of about 6,000 inhabitants in southern Poland in the Silesian Voivodeship, situated southwest of Kraków, in the vicinity of Bielsko-Biała.
